				I already have a post im responding to the question about factions.  Kill orcs in crushbone for kelethin faction.  Blackburrow gnolls for qeynos faction.  Orcs around Freeport for Freeport faction.  Sarnaks and goblins on kunark for cabilis faction.  Kerrans for Erudite faction. Goblins for Dwarven faction.  Minotaurs for Gnome faction. and on velious u can kill dwarves for giant faction or giants for dwarf faction.  not sure how to get felwithe faction but that about covers it.
